      <h1>Projects</h1>

      <section id="premise">
        <h2>Monitoring price changes around the world</h2>

        <p>
          Pricespot is the mobile application used to gather consumerâs prices and product data for <a href="http://www.premise.com" target="_blank">premise</a>, a company devoted to track macroeconomic and human trends in real time.
        </p>

        <p>
